How to Use

eXo Platform - Version 1.0


Log In page

In order to login to Platform, you need to input a Platformâ€™s host name, username and password before touching on Sign In button



Setting

Touch on the Setting button to show Language Setting dialog



Main Screen

After finishing the login progress, application will move user to the Main Screen



File Application

Touch on Files icon to start Files application



You can perform actions on files and folders by touching on Actions button


Touch on each of file item to view


Messenger Application

Touch on Messenger icon to start Messenger application



Touch on each of user item in the list to move to the chat window


Gadget

Touch on the DashBoard item to enter the Gadget List



Touch on any Gadget item to start
